  <widget class="QTextEdit" name="textEditSeno">
   <property name="geometry">
    <rect>
     <x>10</x>
     <y>40</y>
     <width>511</width>
     <height>361</height>
    </rect>
   </property>
   <property name="font">
    <font>
     <family>Segoe UI</family>
    </font>
   </property>
   <property name="cursor" stdset="0">
    <cursorShape>ArrowCursor</cursorShape>
   </property>
   <property name="styleSheet">
    <string notr="true">border: none</string>
   </property>
   <property name="readOnly">
    <bool>true</bool>
   </property>
   <property name="html">
    <string>&lt;!DOCTYPE HTML PUBLIC &quot;-//W3C//DTD HTML 4.0//EN&quot; &quot;http://www.w3.org/TR/REC-html40/strict.dtd&quot;&gt;
&lt;html&gt;&lt;head&gt;&lt;meta name=&quot;qrichtext&quot; content=&quot;1&quot; /&gt;&lt;style type=&quot;text/css&quot;&gt;
p, li { white-space: pre-wrap; }
&lt;/style&gt;&lt;/head&gt;&lt;body style=&quot; font-family:'Segoe UI'; font-size:8.25pt; font-weight:400; font-style:normal;&quot;&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot; margin-top:14px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-size:12pt; font-weight:600;&quot;&gt;Texto:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot; margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-size:12pt;&quot;&gt;O seno é uma função trigonométrica fundamental em geometria e trigonometria, relacionada ao ângulo de um triângulo retângulo. No triângulo retângulo, o seno de um ângulo é a razão entre o comprimento do cateto oposto ao ângulo e o comprimento da hipotenusa.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot; margin-top:14px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-size:12pt; font-weight:600;&quot;&gt;Fórmula:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot; margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-size:12pt;&quot;&gt;A fórmula do seno em um triângulo retângulo é:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot; margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-size:12pt;&quot;&gt;	            &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-size:12pt; font-weight:600; font-style:italic;&quot;&gt;sin(θ)= cateto oposto / hipotenusa&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot; margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-size:12pt;&quot;&gt;Onde:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul style=&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; -qt-list-indent: 1;&quot;&gt;&lt;li style=&quot; font-size:12pt;&quot; style=&quot; margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-weight:600;&quot;&gt;θ&lt;/span&gt; é o ângulo. &lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot; font-size:12pt;&quot; style=&quot; margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-weight:600;&quot;&gt;Cateto oposto&lt;/span&gt; é o lado oposto ao ângulo. &lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot; font-size:12pt;&quot; style=&quot; margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-weight:600;&quot;&gt;Hipotenusa&lt;/span&gt; é o maior lado do triângulo, oposto ao ângulo reto. &lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot; margin-top:14px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-size:12pt; font-weight:600;&quot;&gt;Período e Intervalo:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul style=&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; -qt-list-indent: 1;&quot;&gt;&lt;li style=&quot; font-size:12pt;&quot; style=&quot; margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;&quot;&gt;O seno de um ângulo é uma função &lt;span style=&quot; font-weight:600;&quot;&gt;periódica&lt;/span&gt;, o que significa que ela se repete em intervalos regulares. &lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot; font-size:12pt;&quot; style=&quot; margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;&quot;&gt;O intervalo de valores do seno é sempre entre &lt;span style=&quot; font-weight:600;&quot;&gt;-1 e 1&lt;/span&gt;. &lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot; margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-size:12pt;&quot;&gt;		    &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-size:12pt; font-weight:600; font-style:italic;&quot;&gt;−1≤sin(θ)≤1&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-size:12pt;&quot;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot; margin-top:14px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-size:12pt; font-weight:600;&quot;&gt;Características:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot; margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-size:12pt;&quot;&gt;O seno é uma função suave, que pode ser representada por uma &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-size:12pt; font-weight:600;&quot;&gt;curva senoidal&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-size:12pt;&quot;&gt;. Em um gráfico, ela oscila entre -1 e 1 e tem um período de 360° ou 2π2\pi2π radianos. A função seno é fundamental para descrever &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-size:12pt; font-weight:600;&quot;&gt;ondas&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-size:12pt;&quot;&gt; (como som, luz e outras formas de energia), sendo amplamente utilizada em física, engenharia e análise de sinais.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot; margin-top:14px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-size:12pt; font-weight:600;&quot;&gt;Aplicações:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot; margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-size:12pt;&quot;&gt;O seno é utilizado para resolver problemas em diversas áreas, como:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul style=&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; -qt-list-indent: 1;&quot;&gt;&lt;li style=&quot; font-size:12pt;&quot; style=&quot; margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;&quot;&gt;Cálculos de &lt;span style=&quot; font-weight:600;&quot;&gt;ondas e vibrações&lt;/span&gt; em física. &lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot; font-size:12pt;&quot; style=&quot; margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;&quot;&gt;Análise de &lt;span style=&quot; font-weight:600;&quot;&gt;sistemas elétricos e de telecomunicações&lt;/span&gt;. &lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot; font-size:12pt;&quot; style=&quot; margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-weight:600;&quot;&gt;Arquitetura&lt;/span&gt; e engenharia estrutural para calcular forças e distâncias. &lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot; font-size:12pt;&quot; style=&quot; margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;&quot;&gt;No &lt;span style=&quot; font-weight:600;&quot;&gt;desenvolvimento de gráficos&lt;/span&gt; e animações em computação.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;/body&gt;&lt;/html&gt;</string>
   </property>
  </widget>
